                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430102-name-391" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430102-name-391" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430102-name-391" type="surname" value="HODDY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430102-name-391" type="given" value="CHARLOTTE"></interp>CHARLOTTE HODDY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of John Hoddy, a shoemaker, in Carr-square, Moor-lane. In consequence of information, on Thursday the 29th of Dec., I went up into one of my rooms, and missed two pillows, one sheet, two blankets, a counterpane, and a patch-work quilt off the bed—I went into Carr-square, and saw the policeman—I went with him to the sta<lb></lb>tion, and saw the property there—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
